\n773: - [ ] Test multiple concurrent pushes\n774: - [ Test concurrent build and push\n775: - [ ] Test concurrent read operations\n776: - [ ] Verify no race conditions\n777: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n778: \n779: **Verification**: Run concurrent operation tests\n780: \n781: ---\n782: \n783: ### Task 57: Test DockerService with proxy configuration\n784: - [ ] Test build with HTTP_PROXY build_arg\n785: - [ ] Test build with HTTPS_PROXY build_arg\n786: - [ ] Test build with NO_PROXY build_arg\n787: - [ ] Test push with proxy settings\n788: - [ ] Verify proxy configuration works\n789: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n790: \n791: **Verification**: Run proxy configuration tests\n792: \n793: ---\n794: \n795: ### Task 58: Test DockerService with various image sizes\n796: - [ ] Test with small images (< 10 MB)\n797: - [ ] Test with medium images (10-100 MB)\n798: - [ ] Test with large images (> 100 MB)\n799: - [ ] Test size formatting for all sizes\n800: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n801: \n802: **Verification**: Run tests with various image sizes\n803: \n804: ---\n805: \n806: ### Task 59: Test DockerService with special characters in image names\n807: - [ ] Test image names with hyphens\n808: - [ ] Test image names with underscores\n809: - [ ] Test image names with dots\n810: - [ ] Test image names with slashes\n811: - [ ] Test image names with special tags\n812: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n813: \n814: **Verification**: Run tests with special characters\n815: \n816: ---\n817: \n818: ### Task 60: Test DockerService timeout behavior\n819: - [ ] Test build operation timeout\n820: - [ ] Test push operation timeout\n821: - [ ] Test client initialization timeout\n822: - [ ] Verify timeout errors are handled\n823: - [ ] Verify appropriate error messages\n824: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n825: \n826: **Verification**: Run timeout tests\n827: \n828: ---\n829: \n830: ### Task 61: Verify DockerService security best practices\n831: - [ ] Verify passwords are never logged\n832: - [ ] Verify credentials are not stored in instance variables\n833: - [ ] Verify sensitive data is not exposed in errors\n834: - [ ] Verify path traversal is prevented\n835: - [ ] Verify input validation is comprehensive\n836: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n837: \n838: **Verification**: Review security practices\n839: \n840: ---\n841: \n842: ### Task 62: Test DockerService with invalid inputs\n843: - [ ] Test with None values for required parameters\n844: - [ ] Test with empty strings\n845: - [ ] Test with invalid types\n846: - [ ] Test with malformed paths\n847: - [ ] Verify appropriate exceptions are raised\n848: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n849: \n850: **Verification**: Run invalid input tests\n851: \n852: ---\n853: \n854: ### Task 63: Test DockerService backward compatibility\n855: - [ ] Test with old Docker API versions\n856: - [ ] Test with deprecated features if any\n857: - [ ] Verify compatibility with existing code\n858: - [ ] Verify no breaking changes\n859: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n860: \n861: **Verification**: Run backward compatibility tests\n862: \n863: ---\n864: \n865: ### Task 64: Test DockerService performance\n866: - [ ] Measure initialization time\n867: - [ ] Measure build operation time\n868: - [ ] Measure push operation time\n869: - [ ] Measure remove operation time\n870: - [ ] Verify performance is acceptable\n871: - [ ] Identify any performance bottlenecks\n872: - [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n873: \n874: **Verification**: Run performance tests\n875: \n876: ---\n877: \n878: ### Task 65: Final verification and cleanup\n879: - [ ] Run full test suite: `pytest tests/test_docker_service.py -v --cov`\n880: - [ ] Verify all tests pass with >80% coverage\n881: - [ ] Run `flake8 cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` and fix any issues\n882: - [ ] Run `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` and fix any type errors\n883: - [ ] Run `black --check cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` and format if needed\n884: - [ ] Review all code for TODO comments\n885: - [ ] Review all code for FIXME comments\n886: - [ ] Review all code for commented-out code\n887: - [ ] Verify all exported functions have docstrings\n888: - [ ] Verify all exported classes have docstrings\n889: - [ ] Clean up any temporary test files\n890: - [ ] Verify documentation is up to date\n891: - [ ] Verify help text is comprehensive\n892: - [ ] Verify error messages are clear\n893: \n894: **Verification**: All verification steps pass with no errors or warnings\n895: \n896: ---\n897: \n898: ## Summary\n899: \n900: **Total Tasks**: 65\n901: **Estimated Effort**: M (Medium) - 20-30 hours\n902: \n903: ### Key Deliverables\n904: 1. **DockerService Class** - Complete Docker SDK encapsulation\n905: 2. **Build Operations** - Image building with full configuration\n906: 3. **Push Operations** - Registry pushing with authentication\n907: 4. **Image Management** - Image info retrieval and removal\n908: 5. **Error Handling** - Comprehensive error handling and logging\n909: 6. **Security** - Password protection and input validation\n910: 7. **Comprehensive Tests** - Unit and integration tests\n911: 8. **Documentation** - Complete API documentation and examples\n912: \n913: ### Success Criteria\n914: - All Python files compile without errors\n915: - All unit tests pass with >80% code coverage\n916: - All integration tests pass (if Docker is available)\n917: - DockerService initializes correctly with verbose flag\n918: - check_docker_available returns correct boolean\n919: - build_image works with various configurations\n920: - get_image_info returns correct image metadata\n921: - push_image works with and without authentication\n922: - remove_image works correctly\n923: - Error handling is comprehensive with clear messages\n924: - Verbose mode provides detailed logging\n925: - Passwords are never logged or exposed\n926: - Code passes static analysis (flake8, mypy, black)\n927: - Documentation is complete and accurate\n928: - Integration with BuildRuntime works correctly\n929: - Integration with PublishRuntime works correctly\n930: \n931: ### Dependencies\n932: - Python 3.10+\n933: - docker >=6.0.0\n934: - pytest (for testing)\n935: - flake8 (for linting)\n936: - mypy (for type checking)\n937: - black (for formatting)\n938: - Docker daemon (for integration tests)\n939: \n940: ### Blocked By\n941: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n942: \n943: ### Blocks\n944: - None\n945: \n946: ### Notes\n947: - DockerService is a core service used by BuildRuntime and PublishRuntime\n948: - All operations are designed to be idempotent\n949: - Lazy initialization ensures Docker client is only created when needed\n950: - Verbose mode provides detailed logging for debugging\n951: - Security best practices ensure credentials are never exposed\n952: - Comprehensive test coverage ensures reliability\n953: - Error handling provides clear, actionable messages\n954: - The service is thread-safe for read operations\n955: - Write operations should be serialized to avoid race conditions\n\n(End of file - total 955 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024 — DockerService 封装 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `cmd/cli`\n**Language**: Python\n**Size**: M\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify DockerService class structure and initialization\n- [ ] Verify DockerService class exists in agentcube/services/docker_service.py\n- [ ] Verify __init__ method with verbose parameter\n- [ ] Verify verbose flag is stored as instance variable\n- [ ] Verify logging configuration based on verbose flag\n- [ ] Verify lazy initialization of _client property\n- [ ] Verify class docstring describes functionality\n- [ ] Verify imports are correct (docker, logging, time, pathlib, typing)\n\n**Verification**: Run `python -c \"from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService; s = DockerService(verbose=True); print(s)\"` and verify it instantiates correctly\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775871258521,"end":1775871258535}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871258541,"sessionID":"ses_285d35baeffenWjdb48dAJwLcJ","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2ced1e001JwtB3xhnhY6fJP","messageID":"msg_d7a2cdb26001ktT6FlcOyXuEdb","sessionID":"ses_285d35baeffenWjdb48dAJwLcJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-33a3d919727649ad8f383ff89fc77b72","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-024 — DockerService 封装 (DockerService Encapsulation)\n2: \n3: ## 模块信息\n4: \n5: - **模块**: `cmd/cli`\n6: - **语言**: Python\n7: - **规模**: M\n8: - **关联需求**: AR-024\n9: \n10: ## 架构概述\n11: \n12: ### 设计目标\n13: \n14: DockerService 是一个封装了 Docker SDK 操作的服务类，为 AgentCube CLI 的构建和发布工作流提供统一的 Docker 接口。该服务封装了 Docker SDK 的复杂性，提供了简洁的高级 API 用于镜像构建、推送、标记和管理等操作，同时提供完善的错误处理、日志记录和输入验证机制。\n15: \n16: ### 核心组件\n17: \n18: ```\n19: agentcube/services/\n20: ├── docker_service.py         # DockerService 主要实现\n21: ├── __init__.py               # 服务包导出\n22: └── [exceptions.py]           # 自定义异常类（可选）\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### 架构原则\n26: \n27: 1. **封装复杂性**: 将 Docker SDK 的复杂性封装在服务层，提供简洁的高级 API\n28: 2. **延迟初始化**: Docker 客户端采用延迟初始化（Lazy Initialization）模式\n29: 3. **错误隔离**: 将 Docker SDK 异常包装为服务特定异常，避免直接暴露底层实现\n30: 4. **安全第一**: 妥善处理敏感信息（如密码），不记录到日志中\n31: 5. **可观测性**: 提供可选的详细日志模式，支持调试和故障排查\n32: 6. **幂等性**: 所有操作设计为幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\n33: \n34: ## 组件设计\n35: \n36: ### DockerService 类\n37: \n38: #### 数据结构\n39: \n40: ```python\n41: import logging\n42: import time\n43: from pathlib import Path\n44: from typing import Any, Dict, Optional\n45: \n46: import docker\n47: from docker.errors import DockerException\n48: \n49: \n50: logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n51: \n52: \n53: class DockerService:\n54:     \"\"\"Service for Docker operations.\"\"\"\n55: \n56:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n57:         \"\"\"Initialize the Docker service.\n58: \n59:         Args:\n60:             verbose: Enable verbose logging for debugging.\n61: \n62:         Raises:\n63:             RuntimeError: If Docker client initialization fails.\n64:         \"\"\"\n65:         self.verbose = verbose\n66:         if verbose:\n67:             logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)\n68:         self._client: Optional[docker.DockerClient] = None\n69: \n70:     @property\n71:     def client(self) -> docker.DockerClient:\n72:         \"\"\"Get or create Docker client using lazy initialization.\n73: \n74:         Returns:\n75:             The Docker client instance.\n76: \n77:         Raises:\n78:             DockerException: If Docker daemon is not available.\n79:         \"\"\"\n80:         if self._client is None:\n81:             self._client = docker.from_env()\n82:         return self._client\n83: ```\n84: \n85: #### 公共 API 方法\n86: \n87: ##### 1. Docker 可用性检查\n88: \n89: ```python\n90: def check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n91:     \"\"\"Check if Docker daemon is available and running.\n92: \n93:     Returns:\n94:         True if Docker is available, False otherwise.\n95: \n96:     Note:\n97:         This method does not raise exceptions on failure, making it\n98:         suitable for availability checks before operations.\n99:     \"\"\"\n100:     try:\n101:         self.client.ping()\n102:         return True\n103:     except DockerException as e:\n104:         logger.warning(f\"Docker not available: {e}\")\n105:         return False\n106: ```\n107: \n108: ##### 2. 镜像构建\n109: \n110: ```python\n111: def build_image(\n112:     self,\n113:     dockerfile_path: Path,\n114:     context_path: Path,\n115:     image_name: str,\n116:     tag: str = \"latest\",\n117:     build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n118: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n119:     \"\"\"Build a Docker image from a Dockerfile.\n120: \n121:     Args:\n122:         dockerfile_path: Path to the Dockerfile.\n123:         context_path: Path to the build context directory.\n124:         image_name: Name for the resulting image.\n125:         tag: Tag for the image (default: \"latest\").\n126:         build_args: Optional build arguments for proxy configuration.\n127: \n128:     Returns:\n129:         Dict containing:\n130:             - image_name: Full image name with tag.\n131:             - image_id: SHA256 hash of the image.\n132:             - image_size: Human-readable size string.\n133:             - size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n134:             - build_time: Timestamp of the build.\n135: \n136:     Raises:\n137:         FileNotFoundError: If dockerfile_path or context_path does not exist.\n138:         ValueError: If image_name or dockerfile_path is invalid.\n139:         RuntimeError: If Docker is not available or build fails.\n140:     \"\"\"\n141:     if not self.check_docker_available():\n142:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n143: \n144:     logger.info(f\"Building image {image_name}:{tag} from {dockerfile_path}\")\n145:     full_image_name = f\"{image_name}:{tag}\"\n146: \n147:     try:\n148:         image, build_logs = self.client.images.build(\n149:             path=str(context_path),\n150:             dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path),\n151:             tag=full_image_name,\n152:             buildargs=build_args,\n153:             rm=True,\n154:             forcerm=True,\n155:         )\n156: \n157:         image_info = self.get_image_info(full_image_name)\n158:         image_info[\"build_time\"] = time.time()\n159: \n160:         return image_info\n161: \n162:     except DockerException as e:\n163:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to build Docker image: {e}\") from e\n164: ```\n165: \n166: ##### 3. 镜像信息查询\n167: \n168: ```python\n169: def get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n170:     \"\"\"Get detailed information about a Docker image.\n171: \n172:     Args:\n173:         image_name: Name of the image (with or without tag).\n174: \n175:     Returns:\n176:         Dict containing:\n177:             - image_name: The image name.\n178:             - image_id: SHA256 hash (first 12 characters).\n179:             - image_size: Human-readable size string.\n180:             - size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n181: \n182:     Note:\n183:         Returns empty dict if image is not found.\n184:     \"\"\"\n185:     try:\n186:         image = self.client.images.get(image_name)\n187:         attrs = image.attrs\n188: \n189:         image_id = attrs[\"Id\"].split(\":\")[-1][:12]\n190:         size_bytes = attrs.get(\"Size\", 0)\n191: \n192:         return {\n193:             \"image_name\": image_name,\n194:             \"image_id\": image_id,\n195:             \"image_size\": self._format_size(size_bytes),\n196:             \"size_bytes\": size_bytes,\n197:         }\n198: \n199:     except DockerException as e:\n200:         logger.warning(f\"Failed to get image info for {image_name}: {e}\")\n201:         return {}\n202: ```\n203: \n204: ##### 4. 镜像推送\n205: \n206: ```python\n207: def push_image(\n208:     self,\n209:     image_name: str,\n210:     registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n211:     username: Optional[str] = None,\n212:     password: Optional[str] = None,\n213: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n214:     \"\"\"Push a Docker image to a container registry.\n215: \n216:     Args:\n217:         image_name: Local image name to push.\n218:         registry_url: Optional registry URL (e.g., \"registry.example.com/username\").\n219:         username: Optional username for private registry authentication.\n220:         password: Optional password for private registry authentication.\n221: \n222:     Returns:\n223:         Dict containing:\n224:             - pushed_image: Full name of the pushed image.\n225:             - push_time: Timestamp of the push operation.\n226: \n227:     Raises:\n228:         RuntimeError: If Docker is not available, authentication fails,\n229:                      or push operation fails.\n230:         ValueError: If image does not exist locally.\n231: \n232:     Security Note:\n233:         Passwords are never logged or stored in instance variables.\n234:     \"\"\"\n235:     if not self.check_docker_available():\n236:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n237: \n238:     target_image = image_name\n239:     if registry_url:\n240:         target_image = f\"{registry_url}/{image_name}\"\n241:         self._tag_image_sdk(image_name, target_image)\n242: \n243:     if username and password:\n244:         self._docker_login_sdk(registry_url, username, password)\n245: \n246:     logger.info(f\"Pushing image {target_image}\")\n247: \n248:     try:\n249:         push_logs = self.client.images.push(target_image, stream=True, decode=True)\n250: \n251:         for line in push_logs:\n252:             if \"error\" in line:\n253:                 raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to push image: {line['error']}\")\n254:             if self.verbose:\n255:                 logger.debug(f\"Push log: {line}\")\n256: \n257:         return {\n258:             \"pushed_image\": target_image,\n259:             \"push_time\": str(time.time()),\n260:         }\n261: \n262:     except DockerException as e:\n263:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to push Docker image: {e}\") from e\n264: ```\n265: \n266: ##### 5. 镜像删除\n267: \n268: ```python\n269: def remove_image(self, image_name: str, force: bool = True) -> bool:\n270:     \"\"\"Remove a Docker image from the local daemon.\n271: \n272:     Args:\n273:         image_name: Name of the image to remove.\n274:         force: Force removal even if image is in use (default: True).\n275: \n276:     Returns:\n277:         True if removal succeeded, False otherwise.\n278: \n279:     Note:\n280:         This method does not raise exceptions for non-existent images,\n281:         making it safe for cleanup operations.\n282:     \"\"\"\n283:     try:\n284:         self.client.images.remove(image_name, force=force)\n285:         logger.info(f\"Removed image {image_name}\")\n286:         return True\n287:     except DockerException as e:\n288:         logger.warning(f\"Failed to remove image {image_name}: {e}\")\n289:         return False\n290: ```\n291: \n292: #### 私有辅助方法\n293: \n294: ##### 1. Docker registry 登录\n295: \n296: ```python\n297: def _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None:\n298:     \"\"\"Log in to a Docker registry.\n299: \n300:     Args:\n301:         registry: Registry URL or None for Docker Hub.\n302:         username: Username for authentication.\n303:         password: Password for authentication.\n304: \n305:     Raises:\n306:         RuntimeError: If authentication fails.\n307: \n308:     Security Note:\n309:         Password is never logged. Authentication is handled\n310:         securely through Docker SDK.\n311:     \"\"\"\n312:     try:\n313:         self.client.login(username=username, password=password, registry=registry)\n314:         logger.info(f\"Successfully logged in to registry: {registry or 'default'}\")\n315:     except DockerException as e:\n316:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to log in to Docker registry: {e}\") from e\n317: ```\n318: \n319: ##### 2. 镜像标记\n320: \n321: ```python\n322: def _tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> None:\n323:     \"\"\"Tag a Docker image with a new name.\n324: \n325:     Args:\n326:         source_image: Existing image name.\n327:         target_image: New image name/tag.\n328: \n329:     Raises:\n330:         RuntimeError: If tagging fails.\n331:     \"\"\"\n332:     try:\n333:         image = self.client.images.get(source_image)\n334:         image.tag(target_image, force=True)\n335:         logger.info(f\"Tagged {source_image} as {target_image}\")\n336:     except DockerException as e:\n337:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to tag Docker image: {e}\") from e\n338: ```\n339: \n340: ##### 3. 大小格式化\n341: \n342: ```python\n343: def _format_size(self, size_bytes: int) -> str:\n344:     \"\"\"Format byte size into human-readable format.\n345: \n346:     Args:\n347:         size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n348: \n349:     Returns:\n350:         Human-readable size string (e.g., \"2.00 GB\").\n351: \n352:     Example:\n353:         >>> self._format_size(2147483648)\n354:         \"2.00 GB\"\n355:     \"\"\"\n356:     size = float(size_bytes)\n357:     for unit in [\"B\", \"KB\", \"MB\", \"GB\"]:\n358:         if size < 1024:\n359:             return f\"{size:.2f} {unit}\"\n360:         size /= 1024\n361:     return f\"{size:.2f} TB\"\n362: ```\n363: \n364: ## 数据流\n365: \n366: ### 镜像构建流程\n367: \n368: ```\n369: ┌─────────────────┐\n370: │ BuildRuntime    │\n371: │ (调用方)        │\n372: └────────┬────────┘\n373:          │\n374:          ▼\n375: ┌─────────────────┐\n376: │ build_image()   │\n377: │ DockerService   │\n378: └────────┬────────┘\n379:          │\n380:          ├─────────────────────────────────┐\n381:          │                                 │\n382:          ▼                                 ▼\n383: ┌─────────────────┐              ┌─────────────────┐\n384: │ check_docker_   │              │ validate_paths()│\n385: │ available()     │              │                 │\n386: └────────┬────────┘              └────────┬────────┘\n387:          │                                 │\n388:          ▼                                 ▼\n389:      ┌────┴────┐                    ┌──────┴──────┐\n390:      │         │                    │             │\n391:      ▼         ▼                    ▼             ▼\n392:  ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐           ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n393:  │可用? │  │不可用?│          │路径有效? │  │路径无效? │\n394:  └───┬──┘  └───┬──┘           └────┬─────┘  └────┬─────┘\n395:      │          │                    │             │\n396:      ▼          ▼                    ▼             ▼\n397:  ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐            ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n398:  │继续  │  │抛出   │            │调用      │  │抛出      │\n399:  │构建  │  │Runtime│            │Docker    │  │FileNotFound│\n400:  └───┬──┘  └──────┘            │SDK.build │  └──────────┘\n401:      │                       └────┬─────┘\n402:      │                            │\n403:      ▼                            ▼\n404: ┌─────────────────┐      ┌─────────────────┐\n405: │ get_image_info()│      │ 流式输出日志    │\n406: │                 │      │ (verbose模式)   │\n407: └────────┬────────┘      └─────────────────┘\n408:          │\n409:          ▼\n410: ┌─────────────────┐\n411: │ 返回结果dict    │\n412: │ (image_id,      │\n413: │  size, time)    │\n414: └─────────────────┘\n415: ```\n416: \n417: ### 镜像推送流程\n418: \n419: ```\n420: ┌─────────────────┐\n421: │ PublishRuntime  │\n422: │ (调用方)        │\n423: └────────┬────────┘\n424:          │\n425:          ▼\n426: ┌─────────────────┐\n427: │ push_image()    │\n428: │ DockerService   │\n429: └────────┬────────┘\n430:          │\n431:          ├─────────────────────────────────┐\n432:          │                                 │\n433:          ▼                                 ▼\n434: ┌─────────────────┐              ┌─────────────────┐\n435: │ check_docker_   │              │ validate_image()│\n436: │ available()     │              │                 │\n437: └────────┬────────┘              └────────┬────────┘\n438:          │                                 │\n439:          ▼                                 ▼\n440:      ┌────┴────┐                    ┌──────┴──────┐\n441:      │         │                    │             │\n442:      ▼         ▼                    ▼             ▼\n443:  ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐           ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n444:  │可用? │  │不可用?│          │镜像存在? │  │镜像不存在?│\n445:  └───┬──┘  └───┬──┘           └────┬─────┘  └────┬─────┘\n446:      │          │                    │             │\n447:      ▼          ▼                    ▼             ▼\n448:  ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐            ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n449:  │检查  │  │抛出   │            │检查      │  │抛出      │\n450:  │registry│ │Runtime│            │是否需要  │  │ValueError│\n451:  │URL?   │  │Error  │            │重新标记  │  │          │\n452:  └───┬──┘  └──────┘            └────┬─────┘  └──────────┘\n453:      │                            │\n454:      ▼                            ▼\n455: ┌──────────┐              ┌───────────────┐\n456: │需要登录? │              │ _tag_image_sdk│\n457: └────┬─────┘              └───────┬───────┘\n458:      │                            │\n459:   ┌──┴──┐                         ▼\n460:   │     │                    ┌──────────────┐\n461:   ▼     ▼                    │需要认证?     │\n462: ┌────┐ ┌────┐                └────┬─────────┘\n463: │是  │ │否  │                     │\n464: └┬───┘ └┬──┘                  ┌────┴────┐\n465:  │     │                      │         │\n466:  ▼     ▼                      ▼         ▼\n467: ┌─────────┐              ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐\n468: │_docker_ │              │是       │ │否       │\n469: │login_sdk│              └────┬────┘ └────┬────┘\n470: └────┬────┘                   │           │\n471:      │                       ▼           ▼\n472:      ▼                  ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐\n473: ┌─────────┐             │_docker_ │  │调用     │\n474: │调用     │             │login_sdk│  │Docker   │\n475: │Docker   │             └────┬────┘  │SDK.push │\n476: │SDK.push │                  │       └────┬────┘\n477: └────┬────┘                  ▼            │\n478:      │                 ┌─────────┐        │\n479:      ▼                 │调用     │        │\n480: ┌─────────┐            │Docker   │        ▼\n481: │流式输出 │            │SDK.push │  ┌─────────────┐\n482: │日志     │            └────┬────┘  │验证推送结果 │\n483: │(verbose)│                 │       └──────┬──────┘\n484: └─────────┘                 ▼              │\n485:                    ┌─────────────┐          │\n486:                    │流式输出日志  │          │\n487:                    │(verbose)     │          ▼\n488:                    └─────────────┘  ┌─────────────┐\n489:                                     │返回结果dict │\n490:                                     └─────────────┘\n491: ```\n492: \n493: ## 序列图\n494: \n495: ### 成功构建镜像\n496: \n497: ```\n498: BuildRuntime    DockerService    Docker Client    Docker Daemon\n499:      │                 │                 │                  │\n500:      │ build_image()   │                 │                  │\n501:      │────────────────►│                 │                  │\n502:      │                 │ check_docker_   │                  │\n503:      │                 │ available()     │                  │\n504:      │                 │────────────────►│                  │\n505:      │                 │                 │ ping()           │\n506:      │                 │                 │─────────────────►│\n507:      │                 │                 │◄─────────────────│\n508:      │                 │◄────────────────│                  │\n509:      │                 │ images.build()  │                  │\n510:      │                 │────────────────►│                  │\n511:      │                 │                 │ build context    │\n512:      │                 │                 │─────────────────►│\n513:      │                 │                 │◄─────────────────│\n514:      │                 │                 │ (stream logs)    │\n515:      │                 │◄────────────────│                  │\n516:      │                 │ get_image_info()│                  │\n517:      │                 │────────────────►│                  │\n518:      │                 │                 │ images.get()     │\n519:      │                 │                 │─────────────────►│\n520:      │                 │                 │◄─────────────────│\n521:      │                 │◄────────────────│                  │\n522:      │◄────────────────│                 │                  │\n523:      │  result dict    │                 │                  │\n524: ```\n525: \n526: ### 推送镜像到私有仓库\n527: \n528: ```\n529: PublishRuntime  DockerService    Docker Client    Docker Daemon   Registry\n530:       │                │                 │                  │           │\n531:       │ push_image()   │                 │                  │           │\n532:       │───────────────►│                 │                  │           │\n533:       │                │ check_docker_   │                  │           │\n534:       │                │ available()     │                  │           │\n535:       │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n536:       │                │                 │ ping()           │           │\n537:       │                │                 │─────────────────►│           │\n538:       │                │                 │◄─────────────────│           │\n539:       │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n540:       │                │ _tag_image_sdk()│                  │           │\n541:       │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n542:       │                │                 │ image.tag()      │           │\n543:       │                │                 │─────────────────►│           │\n544:       │                │                 │◄─────────────────│           │\n545:       │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n546:       │                │ _docker_login_  │                  │           │\n547:       │                │ sdk()           │                  │           │\n548:       │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n549:       │                │                 │ login()          │           │\n550:       │                │                 │─────────────────────────────►│\n551:       │                │                 │◄─────────────────────────────│\n552:       │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n553:       │                │ images.push()   │                  │           │\n554:       │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n555:       │                │                 │ push layers      │           │\n556:       │                │                 │─────────────────────────────►│\n557:       │                │                 │◄─────────────────────────────│\n558:       │                │                 │ (stream logs)    │           │\n559:       │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n560:       │◄───────────────│                 │                  │           │\n561:       │  result dict   │                 │                  │           │\n562: ```\n563: \n564: ## 错误处理\n565: \n566: ### 错误分类\n567: \n568: | 错误类型 | 异常类 | 触发场景 | 处理策略 |\n569: |---------|--------|---------|---------|\n570: | Docker 不可用 | `RuntimeError` | `check_docker_available()` 返回 `False` | 操作前检查，提供清晰错误信息 |\n571: | 文件不存在 | `FileNotFoundError` | dockerfile_path 或 context_path 不存在 | 验证输入路径，提供路径信息 |\n572: | 镜像不存在 | `ValueError` | 尝试操作不存在的镜像 | 验证镜像存在性 |\n573: | 构建失败 | `RuntimeError` | Docker 构建过程失败 | 包装 Docker SDK 异常 |\n574: | 认证失败 | `RuntimeError` | Registry 认证失败 | 不记录密码，提供通用错误信息 |\n575: | 网络错误 | `RuntimeError` | Registry 不可达 | 提供网络相关信息 |\n576: | 标记失败 | `RuntimeError` | 镜像标记失败 | 提供源/目标镜像名称 |\n577: \n578: ### 异常处理策略\n579: \n580: ```python\n581: def _handle_docker_exception(self, operation: str, exception: DockerException) -> None:\n582:     \"\"\"Handle Docker SDK exceptions with context.\n583: \n584:     Args:\n585:         operation: Name of the operation being performed.\n586:         exception: The Docker SDK exception.\n587: \n588:     Raises:\n589:         RuntimeError: Wrapped exception with additional context.\n590:     \"\"\"\n591:     error_msg = f\"Docker {operation} failed: {str(exception)}\"\n592:     logger.error(error_msg)\n593:     raise RuntimeError(error_msg) from exception\n594: ```\n595: \n596: ### 错误恢复机制\n597: \n598: 1. **客户端重连**: 如果 Docker 守护进程重启，客户端属性会重新初始化\n599: 2. **幂等操作**: 所有操作设计为可安全重试\n600: 3. **非关键失败**: `remove_image()` 等操作失败不抛出异常，仅返回 `False`\n601: \n602: ## 安全考虑\n603: \n604: ### 凭证处理\n605: \n606: ```python\n607: def _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None:\n608:     \"\"\"Secure login to Docker registry.\n609: \n610:     Security Measures:\n611:         1. Password is never logged or stored in instance variables.\n612:         2. Uses Docker SDK's secure authentication mechanism.\n613:         3. Password is only held in memory during the login call.\n614:         4. Log messages use placeholders for sensitive data.\n615:     \"\"\"\n616:     try:\n617:         # Password is only passed to Docker SDK, never logged\n618:         self.client.login(username=username, password=password, registry=registry)\n619: \n620:         # Log success without revealing credentials\n621:         registry_name = registry or \"Docker Hub\"\n622:         logger.info(f\"Successfully logged in to registry: {registry_name}\")\n623:     except DockerException as e:\n624:         # Error message does not include password\n625:         raise RuntimeError(\n626:             f\"Failed to log in to Docker registry '{registry or 'Docker Hub'}': {e}\"\n627:         ) from e\n628: ```\n629: \n630: ### 路径验证\n631: \n632: ```python\n633: def _validate_build_paths(self, dockerfile_path: Path, context_path: Path) -> None:\n634:     \"\"\"Validate file paths before Docker operations.\n635: \n636:     Security Measures:\n637:         1. Resolves absolute paths to prevent directory traversal.\n638:         2. Validates paths exist before operations.\n639:         3. Validates context_path is a directory.\n640:         4. Validates dockerfile_path is a file.\n641: \n642:     Raises:\n643:         FileNotFoundError: If paths do not exist.\n644:         ValueError: If paths have invalid types.\n645:     \"\"\"\n646:     dockerfile_path = dockerfile_path.resolve()\n647:     context_path = context_path.resolve()\n648: \n649:     if not dockerfile_path.exists():\n650:         raise FileNotFoundError(f\"Dockerfile not found: {dockerfile_path}\")\n651:     if not dockerfile_path.is_file():\n652:         raise ValueError(f\"Dockerfile path is not a file: {dockerfile_path}\")\n653: \n654:     if not context_path.exists():\n655:         raise FileNotFoundError(f\"Build context not found: {context_path}\")\n656:     if not context_path.is_dir():\n657:         raise ValueError(f\"Build context path is not a directory: {context_path}\")\n658: ```\n659: \n660: ### 日志安全\n661: \n662: ```python\n663: # Good: No sensitive information\n664: logger.info(f\"Pushing image {target_image}\")\n665: logger.info(f\"Successfully logged in to registry: {registry_name}\")\n666: \n667: # Bad: Never log passwords\n668: # logger.info(f\"Logging in with password: {password}\")  # DON'T DO THIS\n669: ```\n670: \n671: ## API 契约\n672: \n673: ### 公共 API 摘要\n674: \n675: | 方法 | 输入参数 | 返回值 | 可能抛出 |\n676: |------|---------|--------|---------|\n677: | `__init__` | `verbose: bool = False` | `DockerService` 实例 | `RuntimeError` |\n678: | `check_docker_available` | - | `bool` | - |\n679: | `build_image` | `dockerfile_path`, `context_path`, `image_name`, `tag`, `build_args` | `Dict[str, Any]` | `RuntimeError`, `FileNotFoundError`, `ValueError` |\n680: | `get_image_info` | `image_name` | `Dict[str, Any]` | - |\n681: | `push_image` | `image_name`, `registry_url`, `username`, `password` | `Dict[str, Any]` | `RuntimeError`, `ValueError` |\n682: | `remove_image` | `image_name`, `force` | `bool` | - |\n683: \n684: ### 返回值结构\n685: \n686: #### build_image() 返回值\n687: \n688: ```python\n689: {\n690:     \"image_name\": \"myagent:latest\",\n691:     \"image_id\": \"abc123def456\",\n692:     \"image_size\": \"2.00 GB\",\n693:     \"size_bytes\": 2147483648,\n694:     \"build_time\": 1712851200.123456\n695: }\n696: ```\n697: \n698: #### push_image() 返回值\n699: \n700: ```python\n701: {\n702:     \"pushed_image\": \"registry.example.com/username/myagent:latest\",\n703:     \"push_time\": \"1712851200.123456\"\n704: }\n705: ```\n706: \n707: #### get_image_info() 返回值\n708: \n709: ```python\n710: {\n711:     \"image_name\": \"myagent:latest\",\n712:     \"image_id\": \"abc123def456\",\n713:     \"image_size\": \"2.00 GB\",\n714:     \"size_bytes\": 2147483648\n715: }\n716: ```\n717: \n718: ## 依赖项\n719: \n720: | 依赖 | 版本 | 用途 |\n721: |------|------|------|\n722: | `docker` | `>=6.0.0` | Docker SDK for Python |\n723: | `pathlib` | - | 文件路径处理（标准库） |\n724: | `logging` | - | 日志记录（标准库） |\n725: | `typing` | - | 类型注解（标准库） |\n726: | `time` | - | 时间戳（标准库） |\n727: \n728: ### Docker SDK 依赖\n729: \n730: DockerService 依赖 `docker.from_env()` 初始化客户端，该函数会自动：\n731: \n732: 1. 从环境变量 `DOCKER_HOST` 读取 Docker daemon 地址\n733: 2. 使用默认的 Unix socket 或 Windows named pipe\n734: 3. 支持环境变量配置：\n735:    - `DOCKER_HOST`: Docker daemon 地址\n736:    - `DOCKER_TLS_VERIFY`: TLS 验证\n737:    - `DOCKER_CERT_PATH`: 证书路径\n738: \n739: ## 测试策略\n740: \n741: ### 单元测试\n742: \n743: #### 测试覆盖率目标\n744: \n745: - **行覆盖率**: ≥ 90%\n746: - **分支覆盖率**: ≥ 85%\n747: \n748: #### 测试用例分类\n749: \n750: **1. 初始化测试**\n751: \n752: ```python\n753: def test_docker_service_init_verbose():\n754:     \"\"\"Test DockerService initialization with verbose=True.\"\"\"\n755:     service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n756:     assert service.verbose is True\n757:     assert service._client is None  # Lazy initialization\n758: \n759: def test_docker_service_init_non_verbose():\n760:     \"\"\"Test DockerService initialization with verbose=False.\"\"\"\n761:     service = DockerService(verbose=False)\n762:     assert service.verbose is False\n763: ```\n764: \n765: **2. 可用性检查测试**\n766: \n767: ```python\n768: def test_check_docker_available_success():\n769:     \"\"\"Test successful Docker availability check.\"\"\"\n770:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n771:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n772:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n773:         mock_client.ping.return_value = True\n774: \n775:         service = DockerService()\n776:         assert service.check_docker_available() is True\n777: \n778: def test_check_docker_available_failure():\n779:     \"\"\"Test failed Docker availability check.\"\"\"\n780:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n781:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n782:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n783:         mock_client.ping.side_effect = DockerException(\"Connection failed\")\n784: \n785:         service = DockerService()\n786:         assert service.check_docker_available() is False\n787: ```\n788: \n789: **3. 镜像构建测试**\n790: \n791: ```python\n792: def test_build_image_success():\n793:     \"\"\"Test successful image build.\"\"\"\n794:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n795:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n796:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n797: \n798:         mock_image = mock.Mock()\n799:         mock_image.attrs = {\n800:             'Id': 'sha256:abcdef123456',\n801:             'Size': 1024 * 1024  # 1 MB\n802:         }\n803:         mock_client.images.build.return_value = (mock_image, [])\n804: \n805:         service = DockerService()\n806:         result = service.build_image(\n807:             dockerfile_path=Path(\"Dockerfile\"),\n808:             context_path=Path(\".\"),\n809:             image_name=\"test-image\"\n810:         )\n811: \n812:         assert result['image_name'] == \"test-image:latest\"\n813:         assert result['image_id'] == \"abcdef123456\"\n814:         assert \"build_time\" in result\n815: \n816: def test_build_image_docker_unavailable():\n817:     \"\"\"Test build failure when Docker is unavailable.\"\"\"\n818:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n819:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n820:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n821:         mock_client.ping.side_effect = DockerException(\"Not available\")\n822: \n823:         service = DockerService()\n824: \n825:         with pytest.raises(RuntimeError, match=\"Docker is not available\"):\n826:             service.build_image(\n827:                 dockerfile_path=Path(\"Dockerfile\"),\n828:                 context_path=Path(\".\"),\n829:                 image_name=\"test-image\"\n830:             )\n831: ```\n832: \n833: **4. 镜像推送测试**\n834: \n835: ```python\n836: def test_push_image_with_authentication():\n837:     \"\"\"Test pushing image with registry authentication.\"\"\"\n838:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n839:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n840:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n841: \n842:         mock_client.images.push.return_value = [{'status': 'success'}]\n843: \n844:         service = DockerService()\n845:         result = service.push_image(\n846:             image_name=\"test-image\",\n847:             registry_url=\"registry.example.com/user\",\n848:             username=\"testuser\",\n849:             password=\"testpass\"\n850:         )\n851: \n852:         # Verify login was called\n853:         mock_client.login.assert_called_once_with(\n854:             username=\"testuser\",\n855:             password=\"testpass\",\n856:             registry=\"registry.example.com/user\"\n857:         )\n858: \n859:         # Verify push was called with correct image name\n860:         mock_client.images.push.assert_called_once_with(\n861:             \"registry.example.com/user/test-image\",\n862:             stream=True,\n863:             decode=True\n864:         )\n865: \n866:         assert result['pushed_image'] == \"registry.example.com/user/test-image\"\n867: \n868: def test_push_image_password_not_logged():\n869:     \"\"\"Test that password is never logged during push.\"\"\"\n870:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n871:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n872:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n873: \n874:         mock_client.images.push.return_value = [{'status': 'success'}]\n875: \n876:         service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n877:         result = service.push_image(\n878:             image_name=\"test-image\",\n879:             username=\"testuser\",\n880:             password=\"secret123\"\n881:         )\n882: \n883:         # Verify password was passed to login but never logged\n884:         mock_client.login.assert_called_once()\n885:         assert \"secret123\" not in str(mock_client.login.call_args)\n886: ```\n887: \n888: ### 集成测试\n889: \n890: #### 测试环境要求\n891: \n892: - Docker daemon 运行中\n893: - 测试镜像仓库（可选，用于推送测试）\n894: - 测试 Dockerfile\n895: \n896: #### 集成测试用例\n897: \n898: ```python\n899: def test_build_and_push_integration():\n900:     \"\"\"End-to-end test: build and push image.\"\"\"\n901:     service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n902: \n903:     # Build image\n904:     build_result = service.build_image(\n905:         dockerfile_path=Path(\"test/Dockerfile\"),\n906:         context_path=Path(\"test\"),\n907:         image_name=\"integration-test\"\n908:     )\n909: \n910:     assert build_result['image_name'] == \"integration-test:latest\"\n911: \n912:     # Verify image exists\n913:     image_info = service.get_image_info(\"integration-test:latest\")\n914:     assert image_info['image_name'] == \"integration-test:latest\"\n915: \n916:     # Clean up\n917:     assert service.remove_image(\"integration-test:latest\") is True\n918: ```\n919: \n920: ### Mock 测试策略\n921: \n922: 使用 `unittest.mock` 模拟 Docker SDK：\n923: \n924: ```python\n925: @pytest.fixture\n926: def mock_docker_service():\n927:     \"\"\"Fixture providing a mocked DockerService.\"\"\"\n928:     with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n929:         mock_client = mock.Mock()\n930:         mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n931:         mock_client.ping.return_value = True\n932:         service = DockerService()\n933:         yield service, mock_client\n934: ```\n935: \n936: ## 性能考虑\n937: \n938: ### 内存使用\n939: \n940: 1. **流式处理**: 构建和推送操作使用流式日志，避免将所有输出加载到内存\n941: 2. **延迟初始化**: Docker 客户端只在需要时初始化\n942: 3. **无状态设计**: 方法调用间不保持状态，减少内存占用\n943: \n944: ### 并发处理\n945: \n946: ```python\n947: # DockerService 是线程安全的（只读操作）\n948: # 但不建议并发执行构建或推送操作\n949: # 因为 Docker SDK 本身不是完全线程安全的\n950: \n951: # 推荐：为每个操作创建新的 DockerService 实例\n952: service1 = DockerService()\n953: service2 = DockerService()\n954: \n955: # 或者使用队列串行化操作\n956: from queue import Queue\n957: from threading import Thread\n958: \n959: def build_worker(queue: Queue):\n960:     while True:\n961:         task = queue.get()\n962:         service = DockerService()\n963:         service.build_image(**task)\n964:         queue.task_done()\n965: ```\n966: \n967: ### 超时配置\n968: \n969: 考虑为长时间操作添加超时（未来增强）：\n970: \n971: ```python\n972: def build_image(\n973:     self,\n974:     dockerfile_path: Path,\n975:     context_path: Path,\n976:     image_name: str,\n977:     tag: str = \"latest\",\n978:     build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n979:     timeout: Optional[int] = None,  # 新增：超时配置\n980: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n981:     \"\"\"Build a Docker image with optional timeout.\"\"\"\n982:     # TODO: 实现超时逻辑\n983:     pass\n984: ```\n985: \n986: ## 使用示例\n987: \n988: ### 基本使用\n989: \n990: ```python\n991: from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\n992: from pathlib import Path\n993: \n994: # 创建服务实例\n995: docker_service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n996: \n997: # 检查 Docker 可用性\n998: if not docker_service.check_docker_available():\n999:     print(\"Docker is not available\")\n1000:     exit(1)\n1001: \n1002: # 构建镜像\n1003: build_result = docker_service.build_image(\n1004:     dockerfile_path=Path(\"Dockerfile\"),\n1005:     context_path=Path(\".\"),\n1006:     image_name=\"myagent\",\n1007:     tag=\"v1.0.0\"\n1008: )\n1009: \n1010: print(f\"Built image: {build_result['image_name']}\")\n1011: print(f\"Image ID: {build_result['image_id']}\")\n1012: print(f\"Size: {build_result['image_size']}\")\n1013: \n1014: # 推送到私有仓库\n1015: push_result = docker_service.push_image(\n1016:     image_name=\"myagent:v1.0.0\",\n1017:     registry_url=\"registry.example.com/username\",\n1018:     username=\"myuser\",\n1019:     password=\"mypassword\"\n1020: )\n1021: \n1022: print(f\"Pushed: {push_result['pushed_image']}\")\n1023: ```\n1024: \n1025: ### 在 BuildRuntime 中使用\n1026: \n1027: ```python\n1028: class BuildRuntime:\n1029:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n1030:         self.verbose = verbose\n1031:         self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n1032: \n1033:     def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n1034:         \"\"\"Build agent Docker image.\"\"\"\n1035:         metadata = self._load_metadata(workspace_path)\n1036: \n1037:         build_result = self.docker_service.build_image(\n1038:             dockerfile_path=workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\",\n1039:             context_path=workspace_path,\n1040:             image_name=metadata.agent_name,\n1041:             tag=metadata.version or \"latest\",\n1042:             build_args=options.get(\"build_args\")\n1043:         )\n1044: \n1045:         return build_result\n1046: ```\n1047: \n1048: ### 在 PublishRuntime 中使用\n1049: \n1050: ```python\n1051: class PublishRuntime:\n1052:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None:\n1053:         self.verbose = verbose\n1054:         self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n1055:         self.provider = provider\n1056: \n1057:     def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n1058:         \"\"\"Publish agent to registry or Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n1059:         metadata = self._load_metadata(workspace_path)\n1060: \n1061:         # 准备镜像\n1062:         image_name = self._prepare_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n1063: \n1064:         # 推送镜像\n1065:         push_result = self.docker_service.push_image(\n1066:             image_name=image_name,\n1067:             registry_url=options.get(\"registry_url\"),\n1068:             username=options.get(\"image_username\"),\n1069:             password=options.get(\"image_password\")\n1070:         )\n1071: \n1072:         # 更新元数据\n1073:         metadata.image = {\n1074:             \"name\": push_result[\"pushed_image\"],\n1075:             \"pushed_at\": push_result[\"push_time\"]\n1076:         }\n1077:         self._save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n1078: \n1079:         return push_result\n1080: ```\n1081: \n1082: ## 与其他组件的交互\n1083: \n1084: ### BuildRuntime 使用\n1085: \n1086: | BuildRuntime → DockerService | 说明 |\n1087: |----------------------------|------|\n1088: | `check_docker_available()` | 构建前检查 Docker 可用性 |\n1089: | `build_image()` | 构建代理镜像 |\n1090: | `get_image_info()` | 获取构建结果信息 |\n1091: | `remove_image()` | 清理失败构建的镜像 |\n1092: \n1093: ### PublishRuntime 使用\n1094: \n1095: | PublishRuntime → DockerService | 说明 |\n1096: |-------------------------------|------|\n1097: | `check_docker_available()` | 推送前检查 Docker 可用性 |\n1098: | `push_image()` | 推送镜像到仓库 |\n1099: | `_tag_image_sdk()` | 重新标记镜像用于推送 |\n1100: | `_docker_login_sdk()` | 认证私有仓库 |\n1101: \n1102: ### 与 CLI 的集成\n1103: \n1104: ```python\n1105: # agentcube/cli/main.py\n1106: def build(\n1107:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\"),\n1108:     proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\"),\n1109:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\"),\n1110:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\"),\n1111:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\"),\n1112: ) -> None:\n1113:     \"\"\"Build agent Docker image.\"\"\"\n1114:     try:\n1115:         runtime = BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n1116:         result = runtime.build(\n1117:             workspace_path=Path(workspace),\n1118:             proxy=proxy,\n1119:             cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n1120:             output_path=output\n1121:         )\n1122: \n1123:         console.print(f\"✓ Built {result['image_name']}\")\n1124:         console.print(f\"  Image ID: {result['image_id']}\")\n1125:         console.print(f\"  Size: {result['image_size']}\")\n1126:     except Exception as e:\n1127:         _handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)\n1128: ```\n1129: \n1130: ## 未来增强\n1131: \n1132: ### 短期增强（1-2 个月）\n1133: \n1134: 1. **超时支持**: 为 `build_image()` 和 `push_image()` 添加超时参数\n1135: 2. **进度回调**: 支持进度回调函数，用于 UI 更新\n1136: 3. **多架构构建**: 支持 `--platform` 参数构建多架构镜像\n1137: 4. **构建缓存优化**: 支持 `--cache-from` 和 `--cache-to` 参数\n1138: \n1139: ### 中期增强（3-6 个月）\n1140: \n1141: 1. **并行构建**: 支持并行构建多个镜像\n1142: 2. **构建历史**: 维护构建历史记录\n1143: 3. **镜像分析**: 添加镜像层分析和优化建议\n1144: 4. **安全扫描**: 集成镜像安全扫描（如 Trivy）\n1145: \n1146: ### 长期增强（6-12 个月）\n1147: \n1148: 1. **分布式构建**: 支持远程构建集群\n1149: 2. **构建缓存服务**: 集中式构建缓存服务\n1150: 3. **镜像签名**: 支持镜像签名和验证\n1151: 4. **CI/CD 集成**: 提供更深入的 CI/CD 系统集成\n1152: \n1153: ## 故障排查\n1154: \n1155: ### 常见问题\n1156: \n1157: **问题 1: Docker daemon 不可用**\n1158: \n1159: ```\n1160: RuntimeError: Docker is not available or not running\n1161: ```\n1162: \n1163: **解决方案**:\n1164: 1. 检查 Docker daemon 是否运行：`docker ps`\n1165: 2. 检查 `DOCKER_HOST` 环境变量\n1166: 3. 检查 Docker 服务状态：`sudo systemctl status docker`\n1167: 4. 重启 Docker 服务：`sudo systemctl restart docker`\n1168: \n1169: **问题 2: 构建失败 - 权限错误**\n1170: \n1171: ```\n1172: PermissionError: [Errno 13] Permission denied: 'Dockerfile'\n1173: ```\n1174: \n1175: **解决方案**:\n1176: 1. 检查文件权限：`ls -la Dockerfile`\n1177: 2. 确保当前用户有读取权限\n1178: 3. 检查 Docker 用户组权限\n1179: \n1180: **问题 3: 推送失败 - 认证错误**\n1181: \n1182: ```\n1183: RuntimeError: Failed to log in to Docker registry: unauthorized\n1184: ```\n1185: \n1186: **解决方案**:\n1187: 1. 验证用户名和密码\n1188: 2. 检查仓库 URL 是否正确\n1189: 3. 确认仓库权限设置\n1190: 4. 尝试手动登录：`docker login registry.example.com`\n1191: \n1192: **问题 4: 推送失败 - 网络错误**\n1193: \n1194: ```\n1195: RuntimeError: Failed to push Docker image: connection timeout\n1196: ```\n1197: \n1198: **解决方案**:\n1199: 1. 检查网络连接\n1200: 2. 配置代理（如适用）\n1201: 3. 检查防火墙设置\n1202: 4. 增加超时时间\n1203: \n1204: ### 调试技巧\n1205: \n1206: **启用详细日志**\n1207: \n1208: ```python\n1209: docker_service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n1210: ```\n1211: \n1212: **检查 Docker 日志**\n1213: \n1214: ```bash\n1215: # Linux\n1216: sudo journalctl -u docker -f\n1217: \n1218: # macOS (Docker Desktop)\n1219: open /Applications/Docker.app\n1220: \n1221: # Windows\n1222: Get-Service docker\n1223: ```\n1224: \n1225: **验证 Docker 连接**\n1226: \n1227: ```python\n1228: service = DockerService()\n1229: if service.check_docker_available():\n1230:     print(\"Docker is available\")\n1231: else:\n1232:     print(\"Docker is not available\")\n1233: ```\n1234: \n1235: ## 总结\n1236: \n1237: DockerService 是 AgentCube CLI 的核心组件之一，为构建和发布工作流提供了统一的 Docker 操作接口。其主要特点包括：\n1238: \n1239: 1. **简洁的 API**: 封装 Docker SDK 复杂性，提供简单易用的接口\n1240: 2. **完善的错误处理**: 统一的错误处理策略，清晰的错误信息\n1241: 3. **安全设计**: 妥善处理敏感信息，验证输入参数\n1242: 4. **可观测性**: 支持详细日志模式，便于调试\n1243: 5. **可测试性**: 完善的单元测试和集成测试\n1244: 6. **可扩展性**: 清晰的架构，便于未来功能增强\n1245: \n1246: 通过 DockerService，BuildRuntime 和 PublishRuntime 可以专注于业务逻辑，而将 Docker 操作的复杂性委托给专门的服务层。这种设计提高了代码的可维护性、可测试性和可重用性。\n\n(End of file - total 1246 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-024 — DockerService 封装 (DockerService Encapsulation)\n\n## 模块信息\n\n- **模块**: `cmd/cli`\n- **语言**: Python\n- **规模**: M\n- **关联需求**: AR-024\n\n## 架构概述\n\n### 设计目标\n\nDockerService 是一个封装了 Docker SDK 操作的服务类，为 AgentCube CLI 的构建和发布工作流提供统一的 Docker 接口。该服务封装了 Docker SDK 的复杂性，提供了简洁的高级 API 用于镜像构建、推送、标记和管理等操作，同时提供完善的错误处理、日志记录和输入验证机制。\n\n### 核心组件\n\n```\nagentcube/services/\n├── docker_service.py         # DockerService 主要实现","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775871258519,"end":1775871258538}}}}
